data.value: The Zagrajden eco path is located 30 km away from the village of Banite. It features the largest number of facilities for crossing difficult stretches. The eco path is built over a river. There are many wooden bridges and water pads, the largest being the two waterfalls- Purgatory and the Cornice. The path is circular, the starting point and the ending point is the village Zagrazhden. For those who want to save time and power there is a road built.
